{"tid":2019481,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"浸大生藏雷射筆案 撤控守行為","createTime":"2020-05-16T10:07:51.000Z","updateTime":"2020-05-16T10:46:22.000Z","uid":25558,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":20,"replies":[{"pid":"2b091fbe134ced220150906986701f0d00355adf","tid":2019481,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-16T10:07:51.000Z","msg":"全文<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/20200516/KDQ7GY6EUE7JGXW4U42WPRQUAI/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200516%2FKDQ7GY6EUE7JGXW4U42WPRQUAI%2F&d=IqGrl%2FmL2I6%2Fp6gKwmVM%2Bf3Ut%2FTlF5atQuTXJDR4vuI%3D&h=c33f129e\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200516%2FKDQ7GY6EUE7JGXW4U42WPRQUAI%2F&h=d23f8e13\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/20200516/KDQ7GY6EUE7JGXW4U42WPRQUAI/</a><br />\n<br />\n浸大生藏雷射筆案 撤控守行為<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://static.apple.appledaily.com.hk/images/apple-photos/apple/20200516/large/1589561323_eb0c.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic.apple.appledaily.com.hk%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple%2F20200516%2Flarge%2F1589561323_eb0c.jpg&h=8c36b052&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n一名浸大生昨在屯門法院審訊<br />\n<br />\n【本報訊】浸大男生去年8月在天水圍警署附近管有一支雷射筆，早前被控管有攻擊性武器罪。<br />\n<br />\n案件昨再訊時，控方同意讓男生簽保守行為了事，撤回控罪，事件纏繞男生近九個月，終告一段落。控方更將案中雷射筆歸還給男生，裁判官不禁問：「支雷射筆都畀？」主控輕聲並簡單回應謂：「指示係咁樣。」<br />\n<br />\n被告男生余宗謙（24歲）報稱就讀浸大四年級。控罪指他於去年8月26日在天盛苑天盛商場行人天橋管有。。。。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n控方無交代理由<br />\n<br />\n男生於今年2月24日、亦即相關控罪的起訴限期前兩。。。。。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n控方案情指，案發凌晨現場約有10名黑衣人聚集，有人用雷射筆射。。。。。。。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n律政司回覆查詢時，未有交代詳細撤控理。。。。。。。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n案件編號：TMCC199/20"},{"pid":"959325b30edb77a3dc29ec92cace0f38a6840deb","tid":2019481,"uid":195540,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-16T10:11:55.000Z","msg":"諗起周星子馳套野"},{"pid":"e5d98a825dce8258c6e90886f1c8914ebb4e2317","tid":2019481,"uid":52062,"like":1,"dislike":0,"sc